 a[num](0) is 1. x is 2. 算子返回 true，x becomes 1. num becomes 1. 因为 N==1, loop的i goes to 0到 < 1的条件， so loop runs once. After that, the check:

num==1 == N → yes. x is 1>0 → yes. 因此，num decrements到0, then the code returns 0.
